{"title":"Sword of Cerebov","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Sword_of_Cerebov","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                         |\n| - | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | A twisted blade, covered in eerie flames. Its demonic power burns away some of the fire resistance of those it strikes. |\n\n[![Sword of cerebov.png](/images/e/e0/Sword_of_cerebov.png)](/File:Sword_of_cerebov.png) ***the +6 sword of Cerebov***\n\n+6 flamberge (modified [great sword](/Great_sword \"Great sword\"): 18 damage, -2 accuracy)\n\n[Flaming](/Flaming \"Flaming\") brand  \nInflicts rF- on hit  \n[Evil](/Evil \"Evil\")\n\n## Desirability\n\nThe **sword of Cerebov**[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1) is an [unrand](/Unrand \"Unrand\") sword wielded by [Cerebov](/Cerebov \"Cerebov\"), a [unique](/Unique \"Unique\") [pandemonium lord](/Pandemonium_lord \"Pandemonium lord\"). Foes struck by the sword lose 1 rank of [fire resistance](/Fire_resistance \"Fire resistance\"), which can even make fire-immune foes vulnerable.\n\nOn its own, this sword can be a strong weapon. But by the time you kill Cerebov, there's usually better options available. Even [Long Blades](/Long_Blades \"Long Blades\") users may prefer a +9 [triple sword](/Triple_sword \"Triple sword\") or one-handed sword. [Fire Magic](/Fire_Magic \"Fire Magic\") specialists will often want to blast enemies with big AOE ([Ignition](/Ignition \"Ignition\"), [Fire Storm](/Fire_Storm \"Fire Storm\")), leaving no time to swing in melee. Therefore, it is generally carried as a prize more than anything.\n\n## History\n\n- From [0.19](/0.19 \"0.19\") to [0.28](/0.28 \"0.28\"), the sword of Cerebov had 16 base damage and [riposte](/Riposte \"Riposte\").\n- Prior to [0.13](/0.13 \"0.13\"), the sword of Cerebov was a regular [great sword](/Great_sword \"Great sword\"), and its special effect only ignored fire resistance for the sword's own damage.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [art-data.txt:334](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L334) (0.30.1)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Sword of Cerebov - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Sword_of_Cerebov\",\"wgTitle\":\"Sword of Cerebov\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":75378,\"wgRevisionId\":75378,\"wgArticleId\":4361,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Unrands\",\"Long blades\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Sword_of_Cerebov\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":4361,\"wgRequestId\":\"d4b8db40f6638d97ab267914\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[]});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"us